{"tid":1747510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有留守者稱警方若包圍「一世」　自己亦留理大「一世」","createTime":"2019-11-23T08:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T11:03:44.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"efa4ffbcd290bf4384fd8d40b9f7fb7cc1a8dae2","tid":1747510,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"繼續有人在理大校園留守，一名留守人士在其他人陪同下離開。其中理大學生會署理會長胡國泓表示，考慮今日內離開理大，亦會考慮聯絡校方陪同離開。<br />\n<br />\n他表示作為學生會幹事，有責任照顧留守者的需要，作為橋樑協調外界的支援，所以由上星期三留守至今，但留守人數愈來愈少，當完成任務時會選擇離開。<br />\n<br />\n胡國泓表示，留守者匿藏在不同角落，人數難以估計。他不滿校方反應太遲，在衝突接近完結、校園即將被包圍時才介入，令校方角色十分被動。<br />\n<br />\n另一名仍然留守的示威者表示，覺得自己沒有做錯，所以不會刻意逃走，又指警方若可以包圍理大「一世」，自己亦都能留在理大「一世」。他表示，已經沒有計算逗留在理大的日數，指最初數日捱得住，但隨著其他人逐漸離去，感到頗大打擊。他表示，自己並非理大學生，當日只是進理大飯堂吃飯，之後就被警方包圍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494004-20191123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494004-20191123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=5283dfa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494004-20191123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=48905907\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494004-20191123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"12b99c4167e5f3ddd5131dfd7147d34af8a2cfe7","tid":1747510,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:00:05.000Z","msg":"我要入理大"},{"pid":"5f90d41d18538fa8bc84cf75c7353c376392c418","tid":1747510,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e6da3813d11127d14de9be8cce43a5d0f0fd74","tid":1747510,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:04:42.000Z","msg":"他表示，自己並非理大學生，當日只是進理大飯堂吃飯，之後就被警方包圍。<br />\n<br />\n岩呀<br />\n我入去食飯 有乜錯<br />\n<br />\n正苦咪封紅隊 附近街道 埋工 紅磡站 尖東站 封足佢幾年<br />\n<br />\n仲有正苦 你咪以為可以繼續無止境非法禁錮<br />\n全世界看在眼裡<br />\n非法禁錮<br />\n<br />\n我地手足實搵晒外國問你正苦非法禁錮既原因和理由"},{"pid":"1b15bc11a9718d64c768212cf55a5b5695ee93e1","tid":1747510,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:05:04.000Z","msg":"食個飯都比曱甴話參與暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5873ba91e7813667858d60f1c0de8c74a722bd02","tid":1747510,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5eb0fc3db4313c83326570384afb09cb093b3a9","tid":1747510,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有邊個想係入面被困一世<br />\n幾時先放人呀 死仆街"},{"pid":"3615ed0550952029e21d6ba9f3caf79fcdfa3830","tid":1747510,"uid":303677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b78e8de5284dad3fe4d77e6dbcdfae8a9fc4d6","tid":1747510,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5eb0fc3db4313c83326570384afb09cb093b3a9","tid":1747510,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有邊個想係入面被困一世<br />\n幾時先放人呀 死仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:05:13.000Z","msg":"放人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"h